page.title: 01The Area
page.content: This area is located in Dorset on the north-west boundary of the Borough of Poole. Part of the area lies within Poole but most lies within the county district. The area can be divided into three basic sectors. The eastern sector comprising of residential development. Most of this has taken place since 1950. The western area is basically pastural farming. The central sector can be sub-divided into a residential area and an area of natural sand-heath. This heathland although of scientific interest is under great pressure from developers to extend the light industry and residential area.
